Desecret

Functions to be implemented:

    Monitor the following items:
        1. SMS messages
        2. calls (+recording)
        3. locations
        4. photos

    Export/sync interfaces:
        1. file system
        2. email (e.g., Gmail IMAP interface)
        3. SMS (emergent only)

    Emergent triggers:
        1. specific contacts
        2. specific keywords in SMS message contents
        3. within the radius of specific locations (identified by GPS or cellular data)